description:
Wholesale distributors of commercial machines and equipment not
classified elsewhere. Examples include food service and cooking
equipment, neon signs, balances and scales, lockers, commercial
ovens and microwaves, soda fountain fixtures, store fixtures,
mannequins, vending machines, and equipment used in construction
projects. Such merchants may or may not also rent or lease
equipment.
